\c 24 Simudzai misoro yenyu, masuo! Pisarema raDhavhidhi. 241 Nyika ndeyaJehovha, nokuzara kwayo; Nyika yose navageremo. 2 Nokuti wakaiteya pamusoro pamakungwa, Nokuisimbisa pamusoro penzizi. 3 Ndiani angakwira mugomo raJehovha? Ndiani ungamira panzvimbo yake tsvene? 4 Uyo anamaoko akachena, nomwoyo wakanaka kwazvo; Asingasimudziri mwoyo wake kune zvisina maturo, Neasina kupika nhema.
